      <head>Tom&#xE1;s [Thomas; Tommy] Kornfeld</head>

      <div>
        <p>Son of <ref cRef="kornfeld_felix">Felix Kornfeld</ref>, grandson of <ref
            cRef="kornfeld_emil">Emil Kornfeld</ref> and Jeanette Kornfeld (later <ref cRef="schenker_jeanette">Jeanette Schenker</ref>)
            of Aussig (Austria).</p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <head>Correspondence and Photograph</head>

        <p>Correspondence between Heribert Esser and Tom&#xE1;s survives in photocopy as OJ
          71/10a and 71/21a (1988). A photograph of Tom&#xE1;s, inscribed "Tommy Kornfeld, born
          August 7, 1932, taken on August 7, 1939" survives as OJ 72/9, the photographer being Karl
          Engel, Aussig (originally enclosed with OJ 14/7: letter from Felix Kornfeld to Jeanette Schenker, August 23, 1939).</p>
      </div>
